<h4>Nezikchened: first fight</h4>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
    At the start of the first fight, Nezikchened will drain your prayer. Kill him with recoil and poison. You must kill him fast enough, however, or he will despawn.
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
    {% include monster.html monster=site.data.monsters.nezikchened %}
  </div>
</div>
<hr>
<h4>Three guardians</h4>
<p>To go deeper in the cave, you will have to defeat Ranalph Devere, Irvig Senay and San Tojalon. Recoil and poison.</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
